reviewText: Very pleased, reasonable delivery time. Would recommend to others.
Very enjoyable, explains the origin and behind the scenes work involved with a very unusual art installation. I've been to Waterfire three times. It is well worth experiencing.
I felt like I was really there!
Tells a perfect story of an event that is often a mystery to those looking in. If you've never seen Providence before WaterFire it gives a great insight into that as well

Wonderful insights into the history of WaterFire and it's role in helping to transform Providence. It was inspiring to learn about the hard work, planning, and attention to detail that go into each event. If you have been touched by WaterFire then this movie is great way to keep the fire alive in your heart and mind.
